OL,3,CBomb threat missed for six hours
OL,4,Cbefore airport evacuated
OL,6,FEmergency procedures were then
OL,7,Factivated and the decision was made to
OL,8,Fevacuate the entire terminal building
OL,9,Ffollowing a risk assessment, with the
OL,10,Falarm raised publicly at 6:28am on
OL,11,FWednesday 5 March.
OL,13,FHundreds of passengers were already
OL,14,Fwaiting to board in departures,
OL,15,Falthough no flights had taken off.
OL,17,FThe runway was subsequently closed,
OL,18,Fwith all flights suspended and people
OL,19,Fasked to avoid the area as armed
OL,20,Fpolice secured the scene.
