OL,3,CBomb threat missed for six hours
OL,4,Cbefore airport evacuated
OL,6,FAfter extensive checks, it was deemed
OL,7,Fto be a hoax and Jersey Airport
OL,8,Freopened just after 11am.
OL,10,FAt the time, Operations Director
OL,11,FAshley Maggs described it as a
OL,12,F"significant security incident" that
OL,13,Fstaff were "taking very seriously".
OL,15,FHowever, Deputy Jonathan Renouf says:
OL,16,F"It's deeply concerning that a bomb
OL,17,Fthreat was actually received the night
OL,18,Fbefore and not seen by anybody.
