OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F389A1751285243
OL,3,CBomb threat missed for six hours
OL,4,Cbefore airport evacuated
OL,6,F"That seems to be a major security
OL,7,Fbreach and failure, it should be
OL,8,Finvestigated as a matter of extreme
OL,9,Furgency.
OL,11,F"What I find particularly worrying is
OL,12,Fthat it has taken so much effort and
OL,13,Fso long to find out what has gone on.
OL,14,FI have been asking questions and the
OL,15,Fmedia has been asking questions; the
OL,16,Fbest solution in these circumstances
OL,17,Fis openness and transparency. Instead,
OL,18,Fit looks like we've had an attempt to
OL,19,Fcover it up."
