OL,3,CBomb threat missed for six hours
OL,4,Cbefore airport evacuated
OL,6,FIn response, Mr Maggs confirmed the
OL,7,Fminister's timeline, adding: "We are
OL,8,Funable to give any more details of the
OL,9,Fspecifics of this threat due to laws
OL,10,Fwhich govern aviation security.
OL,12,F"A multi-agency response was conducted
OL,13,Fin accordance with emergency response
OL,14,Fprocedures.
OL,16,F"As with any security incident, we
OL,17,Fcannot comment any further on this
OL,18,Fmatter or actions taken."
